    <img src="/assets/fixed/akai-eie/ASIO4AllOptions.jpg" alt="ASIO4All configuration window" />

    <p><strong>Success!</strong></p>

    <p>
        ASIO is reading my interface just like before.<br />
        Phew!
    </p>

    <img src="/assets/fixed/akai-eie/voice_changer_17.jpg" alt="Final reassembled unit" />

